Crazy pants.

197
00:10:10,000 --> 00:10:11,000
Oh, oh.

198
00:10:12,000 --> 00:10:13,000
Are these aunty?

199
00:10:14,000 --> 00:10:16,000
Yeah. I'll put them back right there.

200
