215
00:11:13,000 --> 00:11:15,000
But when I'm not liked...

216
00:11:16,000 --> 00:11:19,000
Yes, if you try to be proper.

217
00:11:20,000 --> 00:11:21,000
I'll try.

218
00:11:36,000 --> 00:11:39,000
The baby got hurt in the snow.

219
00:11:40,000 --> 00:11:42,000
I had fun inside the backpack.

220
00:11:42,000 --> 00:11:43,000
Nice to hear.

221
00:11:48,000 --> 00:11:49,000
Can't sleep?

222
00:11:51,000 --> 00:11:55,000
I'll sing you a lullaby so you can catch your sleep.

223
00:11:56,000 --> 00:12:04,000
Tukutukulanpaitaani, päkäpäkäpäsiäni, päkäpäkäpuskuripäsiäni...

224
00:12:05,000 --> 00:12:10,000
I can't sleep when you sing. My mother can sing.

225
00:12:10,000 --> 00:12:15,000
I have completely forgotten how to treat small children.

226
00:12:16,000 --> 00:12:18,000
I whined, whined...

227
00:12:20,000 --> 00:12:23,000
You rock the cradle so I can't sleep.

228
00:12:25,000 --> 00:12:30,000
