229
00:12:30,000 --> 00:12:33,000
Help! Earthquake, no!

230
00:12:37,000 --> 00:12:39,000
I knocked myself out.

231
00:12:42,000 --> 00:12:44,000
What was it?

232
00:12:47,000 --> 00:12:49,000
Good morning, Moomin-Pekko!

