254
00:14:10,000 --> 00:14:11,000
No wonder he's gaining weight.

255
00:14:12,000 --> 00:14:15,000
Get out of the room right away, that little moose too. As you already know.

256
00:14:16,000 --> 00:14:17,000
Well, I'm going.

257
00:14:17,000 --> 00:14:19,000
I'll take it anyway. What now?

258
00:14:20,000 --> 00:14:23,000
Then you won't be lying to anyone about these lending cookies.

259
00:14:24,000 --> 00:14:25,000
I'll give you one.

260
00:14:26,000 --> 00:14:27,000
All right.

261
00:14:33,000 --> 00:14:35,000
Gummy Paw, Aren't you sleeping yet?

262
00:14:36,000 --> 00:14:37,000
Moomin Mommy, do you have any secrets?

263
00:14:38,000 --> 00:14:40,000
Oh, secrets. Just a guess.

264
00:14:41,000 --> 00:14:42,000
